title: Bridger Canyon - Additional PUD development potential
name: Bridger Canyon - Additional PUD development potential
description:
Scenario for additional density from planned unit developments, if implemented everywhere in AEPD and RFPD zones in Bridger Canyon.

Assumes that 
- government lands remain undeveloped
- density is the maximum 1-in-20 (available, but not a matter of right)
- existing conservation easements and other restrictions are ignored
